        "title": "feat: add canonical ClawScan verdict fields",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add canonical ClawScan verdict/state fields on skill versions and package releases\n- update the ClawScan prompt, parser, worker, moderation, UI, API, and CLI paths to use `clean` / `review` / `warn` / `malicious`\n- add cursor-based backfills and legacy suspicious cleanup helpers while preserving manual moderation and malicious locks\n\n## Rollout\n1. Merge and deploy this schema-widening PR.\n2. Run cursor backfills:\n   ```bash\n   bunx convex run maintenance:backfillSkillVersionClawScanFields '{\"batchSize\":100}' --prod\n   bunx convex run maintenance:backfillPackageReleaseClawScanFields '{\"batchSize\":100}' --prod\n   ```\n3. Verify canonical fields are populated on relevant `skillVersions` and `packageReleases`.\n4. Verify new ClawScan writes set `clawScanVerdict` / `clawScanState` and do not recreate `isSuspicious`, `flagged.review`, or `flagged.suspicious`.\n5. Run legacy cleanup actions before the schema/index narrowing PR:\n   ```bash\n   bunx convex run maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousSkillFields '{\"batchSize\":100}' --prod\n   bunx convex run maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousDigestFields '{\"batchSize\":100}' --prod\n   bunx convex run maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousPackageScanStatuses '{\"batchSize\":100}' --prod\n   bunx convex run maintenance:cleanupLegacySuspiciousPackageReleaseScanStatuses '{\"batchSize\":100}' --prod\n   ```\n6. Verify manual hidden/quarantined/revoked/removed rows and legacy malicious rows remain blocked.\n7. Merge/deploy the legacy-removal PR after verification passes.\n\nRollback:\n- Keep the widened schema and fix forward or revert behavior without deleting canonical fields.\n- If the follow-up cleanup/removal PR needs rollback, revert only that PR and keep canonical verdict data.\n\n## Test plan\n- `codex review --uncommitted --disable plugins --disable multi_agent --disable memories`\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run ci:types-build`\n- `bun run ci:packages`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx tsc --noEmit`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx vitest run convex/securityScan.test.ts convex/lib/packageSecurity.test.ts --reporter=dot`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx vitest run convex/maintenance.test.ts convex/skills.public.test.ts --testNamePattern \"structured reason codes|manual hidden state|visible pending ClawScan\" --reporter=dot`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx vitest run convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts src/components/SkillSecurityScanResults.test.tsx src/components/DetailSecuritySummary.test.tsx --testNamePattern \"malicious ClawScan verdict|malicious audit outcome|malicious summary|pending ClawScan state|ClawScan rescan\" --reporter=dot`\n",
